<exercise checkit-seed="0000" checkit-slug="P5" checkit-title="Expected Value">
    <statement>
                <p> Blanca is gambling at a roullette wheel. The wheel has 8 equally sized spots. 3 of the spots are winning locations, and the rest are losing. If costs \$13 to play the wheel. If Blanca wins, they get their bet back and they win \$31, otherwise they forfeit their bet. What is the expected value of this gamble?
                </p>
        
    </statement>
    <answer>
        <p>
            The expected value is <m>\frac{3}{8}(31) + \frac{5}{8}(-13) = $3.50</m>
        </p>
    </answer>
</exercise>
